    "body" : "<p>A slight variation on Richards answer but <code>readTree</code> can take a string so you can simplify it to:</p>\n\n<pre><code>ObjectMapper mapper = new ObjectMapper();\nJsonNode actualObj = mapper.readTree(\"{\\\"k1\\\":\\\"v1\\\"}\");\n</code></pre>\n"
