    "body" : "<p>A third variant:</p>\n\n<pre><code>ObjectMapper mapper = new ObjectMapper();\nJsonNode actualObj = mapper.readValue(\"{\\\"k1\\\":\\\"v1\\\"}\", JsonNode.class);\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
